import React from 'react'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

function NavBar() {
    return (
        <>
            <nav>
                <Link to="/">Home</Link>
                <Link to="/about">About</Link>
                <Link to="/contact">Contact</Link>
            </nav>
        </>
    )
}

export default NavBar
